name: The Sacred
description:
Stopping life to observe sometimes seems like a gift, but most of the time it's the need to contemplate the simple things in life, contemplate how much you've walked.
Photo recorded in Machu Picchu Pueblo, a town before the ruins of Machu Picchu. Trip that had the route that had as passages Lima, Cusco, Ollamtaytambo and Machu Picchu Pueblo. Path similar to what the Incas used to do in the past. Today they still preserve the original route for the most adventurous.
